title: Wilson's Tyra Ott talks after winning 3rd straight district tennis title (VIDEO)
text:
By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 13, 2015 12:20 AM, updated October 13, 2015 12:37 AM 
Wilson junior Tyra Ott fought past Notre Dame 's Coco Chen to win her third straight District 11 Class AA tennis championship on Monday afternoon at Lehigh University. 
Ott won the title by a score of 6-3, 6-4 over Chen. 
See what Ott had to say after the match in the video at the top of this post.
